# Fixtures layout

All test fixture **assets** live under repo-root [`ops/fixtures/`](ops/fixtures/). Resolve paths via [`zss/testsupport/fixturepaths.ts`](zss/testsupport/fixturepaths.ts).

## Required

| Domain | Path under `ops/fixtures/` |
|--------|------------------------|
| Lang parity | `lang/parity/` + `manifest.json` |
| Lang integration sources | `lang/scripts/` |
| Lang integration goldens | `lang/integration/` |
| Book corpus | `lang/coolregionsbow/` |
| Memory WASM | `memory/wasm/` |
| Synth | `synth/wasm/`, `synth/daisy/` |
| Wanix WASI | `wanix/` (built `.wasm` gitignored) |
| Harness HTML | `harness/` (Daisy/synth Playwright pages; not in `cafe/public`) |
| Book templates | `content/templates/`; build output `content/dist/` |
| Books (npm) | `books/` |
| E2e repro | `e2e/` |
| Generated training | `generated/training/` |

```typescript
// ✅ GOOD
import { LANG_PARITY_DIR } from 'zss/testsupport/fixturepaths'
path.join(LANG_PARITY_DIR, `${id}.zss`)

// ❌ BAD — co-located fixture trees
path.join(__dirname, '__fixtures__/parity')

// ❌ BAD — legacy paths
'scripts/wanix/hello.wat'
'src/fixtures/example-coolregionsbow.book.json'
```

## Generated vs committed

- Regenerate `ops/fixtures/generated/training/` and `ops/fixtures/e2e/` via existing tasks/scripts.
- Lang/memory/synth goldens: regen via parity/regen tests — do not hand-edit unless fixing the generator.

## Harness code

Embedded loaders in `zss/testsupport/` (e.g. wanix hex bytes) stay in testsupport; they reference `ops/fixtures/wanix/` sources for regen comments only.

See [`ops/fixtures/README.md`](ops/fixtures/README.md) for regen task ids.
